      "end_time": 32.53,
      "start_time": 16.15,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "When you're looking at like the overall success of this, it sounds like, I mean, so it sounds like, you know, that this is, you know, being an organic, it's a bit of a longer term play, you know, we, we say minimum kind of, I mean, minimum, minimum of that 90 day period to even start to see that uptick."
