      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "Will you measure this on, you know, kind of the, the, the functionality of it, you know, having this daily post, having those that, that pricing updated or are you most most focused on that uptick?"
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
