      "start_time": 57.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": "bea3b541-5fa6-4e00-88e5-2897e5f21e03",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "I mean, I would like to see an uptick because I probably would really utilize it in communities that are struggling a little bit more."
