      "start_time": 63.93,
      "recording_attendee_id": "bea3b541-5fa6-4e00-88e5-2897e5f21e03",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "And so hopefully having this piece will also just, you know, help organically with ranking and everything else going on."
