      "recording_attendee_id": "bea3b541-5fa6-4e00-88e5-2897e5f21e03",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "Um But that being said, I understand it's, it's not like, you know, you're not necessarily gonna be driving, you know, direct leads from that."
