      "start_time": 82.95,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Yeah, I just like to get to understand when you're like an understanding of when you're thinking about trialing it, how you're gonna look at the success because, you know, we wanna make sure that we're aligned on what, what success will look like for you."
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
      "recording_id": "1e2d6b7b-06df-4e8f-9016-bd867c1c73b4",
      "end_time": 106.36,
      "start_time": 94.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "And if it's, you know, in 90 days, seeing, you know, a huge boost in your traffic and tons of leads from the chat bot, I would say to you, you know, in full transparency, that's likely not gonna be what you'll see, right?"
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
      "recording_id": "1e2d6b7b-06df-4e8f-9016-bd867c1c73b4",
      "end_time": 112.12,
      "start_time": 106.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "So I just, you know, always important that we align on kind of what your expectation will be when it comes to looking at a pilot."
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
      "recording_id": "1e2d6b7b-06df-4e8f-9016-bd867c1c73b4",
      "end_time": 126.1,
      "start_time": 112.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Um And then the other piece of that is there's we we do offer where if you're looking primarily at functionality, the opportunity, did you just put it live even if it's for 30 days on one property or two properties?"
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
      "recording_id": "1e2d6b7b-06df-4e8f-9016-bd867c1c73b4",
      "end_time": 129.6,
      "start_time": 126.11,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "Just so you can see how the posting looks and the feed looks."
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
      "recording_id": "1e2d6b7b-06df-4e8f-9016-bd867c1c73b4",
      "end_time": 135.66,
      "start_time": 129.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "And then from there, you know, we would have AAA discussion after that 30 days of what a larger scale roll out would look like."
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
      "recording_id": "1e2d6b7b-06df-4e8f-9016-bd867c1c73b4",
      "end_time": 142.56,
      "start_time": 135.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 24,
      "text": "So just thinking through options for you um as far as kind of how you wanna approach giving this a try."
    },
    {
      "id": "817de9c6-281f-4334-b602-0c1d38c072cf",
      "recording_id": "1e2d6b7b-06df-4e8f-9016-bd867c1c73b4",
      "end_time": 153.74,
      "start_time": 142.74,
      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "Um And again, those pilots are more more suited or better suited for for if you're really just looking to see like that functionality piece."
