      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 27,
      "text": "we've, we've seen the shift really with the product in it in the sense that a lot of portfolios like yours are bringing this on for that standardization and brand, like staying on brand across the Google profiles, having all of it be automated taking that piece off of your plate."
