      "recording_attendee_id": "120a62c2-58e6-4527-9ae2-49d7506125d4",
      "order_number": 39,
      "text": "And that's, that's exactly, I mean, that's you pinpoint it right there, like we can take that posting piece off of, you know, whoever's plate, um you know, whoever is doing that obviously."
